legacy.full_text:
Sat down with @Tg1Rai @Bergaminus.
We talked about the #China-#US summit meeting, China-#Italy relations, and the #Palestinian issue.

Thanks for having me @Bergaminus 🤝

Find out my comments below👇🏻 https://t.co/Ugtb8JbQfm

legacy.description: 中国驻意大利大使 Chinese Ambassador to Italy
legacy.name: Jia Guide贾桂德

legacy.full_text: The correct way for 2  major countries to get along w/ each other is to adhere to mutual respect,peaceful coexistence& win-win cooperation. The "San Francisco Vision" embraced at this meeting pointed the way&drawn a blueprint for the sound, steady &sustained growth of 🇨🇳🇺🇸rlts.

legacy.description: 中国驻意大利大使 Chinese Ambassador to Italy
legacy.name: Jia Guide贾桂德

legacy.full_text: It also proves once again that mutual benefit&win-win is the essential characteristics of 🇨🇳🇺🇸relations;dialogue&cooperation is the only right choice for the two countries.

legacy.full_text:
Throughout the 70 years and more since the founding of the People’s Republic, China has not provoked a conflict or war, or occupied a single inch of foreign land.

China is the only major country that has written peaceful development into the Constitution of the country& https://t.co/BfR1NfsDqi

legacy.description: 中国驻意大利大使 Chinese Ambassador to Italy
legacy.name: Jia Guide贾桂德

legacy.full_text:
and the Constitution of the goveraing party, thus making peaceful development a commitment of the nation. It benefits from and safeguards the current international order.

The modernization we are pursuing is not for China alone. We are ready to work w/ all countries

legacy.full_text: to advance global modernization featuring peaceful development, mutually beneficial cooperation and common prosperity.

legacy.full_text: President Xi said China sympathizes deeply with the American people, especially the young, for the sufferings that #Fentanyl has inflicted upon them. He and President Biden have agreed to set up a working group on counternarcotics cooperation and help the U.S. tackle drug abuse. https://t.co/9y4ah1IAoF

legacy.description: 中国驻意大利大使 Chinese Ambassador to Italy

legacy.full_text: To increase exchanges between our peoples, especially between the youth, China is ready to invite 50,000 young Americans to China on exchange and study programs in the next 5 years.

legacy.description: 中国驻意大利大使 Chinese Ambassador to Italy
legacy.name: Jia Guide贾桂德

legacy.full_text:
China’s development is driven by its inherent logic and dynamics. China will not take the old path of colonization and plundering, or the wrong path of seeking hegemony with growing strength.

It does not export its ideology,or engage in ideological confrontation w/ any country. https://t.co/kEB0u6b408

legacy.description: 中国驻意大利大使 Chinese Ambassador to Italy

legacy.full_text:
🇨🇳does not have a plan to surpass or unseat the 🇺🇸. Likewise, the 🇺🇸should not scheme to suppress&contain🇨🇳.

Mutual respect, peaceful coexistence&win-win cooperation are the lessons we learned fr. 50 years of🇨🇳🇺🇸relations as well as the conflicts btw major countries in history.

media.ext_alt_text: File photo of Xi Jinping visiting San Francisco taken in front of the Golden Gate Bridge in 1985.
File photo of Xi Jinping visiting San Francisco taken in front of the Golden Gate Bridge in 1985.

legacy.full_text: Pointing to a photo in his phone with the Golden Gate Bridge in the background, President Biden asked President Xi, “Do you know this young man?” “Oh yes,” said President Xi, “this was 38 years ago.”🌞 https://t.co/r65Em6Z7oS

President Xi recalled his first visit to the U.S. “I stayed at the Dvorchaks in Iowa.” He still remembers their address -- 2911 Bonnie Drive. “That was my first face-to-face contact with the Americans. The days I spent with them are unforgettable. For me, they represent America.”
